\v 24 \x + \xo 24: a \xt Acts 12:12,25; 13:13; 15:37-39; Col 4:10; \xo b \xt Acts 19:29; 27:2; Col 4:10; \xo c \xt Col 4:14; 2Tim 4:10; \xo d \xt Col 4:14; 2Tim 4:11.\x*\sig as do my fellow-workers Mark, Aristarchus, Demas, and Luke.\sig*
